window.bookSummaryJSON = "<p>Unity is strength, but the path of a hero is often traveled alone, especially when friends, comrades and allies have been lost. The weight of responsibility is overwhelming, and there is so much at stake that one might feel compelled to howl at the moon Geala. Unfortunately, this moon is nowhere to be found in the Nether, Inferno or Purgatory, nor can it be seen through the leaden acid clouds of Terrastera or beneath the twisted dome of the continent of Meaz.</p> <p>No matter where you hide, the voice of the Harbinger of Nether will find you: \"Die and await Judgment Day . . . \"</p>"; 
